The '''Minister of Defense''' was the title used under the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] for the civilian [[Commander-in-Chief/Legends|head]] of the [[Republic Military/Legends|Republic Military]] and the [[Ministry of Defense]]. 

During the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]], [[Netus]] held the position. [[Koa Delko]] was minister during the [[Mandalorian Wars]].

